overview:
“Kathy Tennant comes to Weblistic after spending the past 7 years with E.W. Scripps Newspapers Division. Most recently she was Director of Online Advertising at KnoxNews.com, E.W. Scripps’ flagship newspaper website in Knoxville, TN. Prior to her most recent role, she was Classified Multimedia Sales manager, managing real estate, employment and online sales teams for the Knoxville News Sentinel and KnoxNews.com. Her focus is on strategic initiatives which generate revenue and drive website traffic to local online businesses.”

(Source: Weblistic)
